- **Required Bot Scopes**: All Slack functionality depends on having correct bot token scopes configured
- **Scope Configuration Files**:
  - Code: [src/lib/slack.ts](mdc:src/lib/slack.ts) - `slackOAuthConfig.botScopes` array  
